  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    CMA letter to AIB NI on a breach of Directions given under the SME Banking Undertakings
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Letter to AIB NI for non-compliance with Directions given under the Small and Medium sized Enterprises (SME) Banking Undertakings 2002.</p>

  </div>
</div>

